text: Kupang is a village in Tutong District, Brunei. It is a subdivision of Keriam, a mukim (subdistrict) of the district. The community is headed by a village head () and the incumbent is Puasa bin Kula. The postcode for Kupang is TB2941. == References == Category:Populated places in Brunei Category:Villages of Brunei
title: Kupang, Brunei
